<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>OWCS 2026 — Overwatch Champions Series</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">OW<span>CS</span></div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#events">이벤트</a></li>
      <li><a href="#regions">지역</a></li>
      <li><a href="#schedule">일정</a></li>
      <li><a href="#prize">상금</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="nav-cta">지금 시청하기</button>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">2026 시즌 진행 중</div>
    <h1>
      최강자를<br />
      가린다<br />
      <span class="highlight">OWCS 2026</span>
    </h1>
    <p>Overwatch Champions Series — 전 세계 최고의 팀들이 글로벌 무대에서 맞붙는 오버워치 공식 e스포츠 대회</p>
    <div class="hero-buttons">
      <a href="#schedule" class="btn-primary">일정 보기</a>
      <a href="#regions" class="btn-secondary">참가 팀 보기</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div class="stats fade-up">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">4</div>
      <div class="stat-label">참가 지역<br>NA · EMEA · Asia · China</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">11</div>
      <div class="stat-label">파트너 팀<br>역대 최대 규모</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">3</div>
      <div class="stat-label">국제 라이브 이벤트<br>도쿄 · 리야드 · 중국</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-number">$150K</div>
      <div class="stat-label">스테이지 상금<br>NA + EMEA 합산</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- EVENTS -->
  <section class="section fade-up" id="events">
    <div class="section-tag">International Events</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">3개의 글로벌<br>라이브 이벤트</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">전 세계 팬들이 현장에서 함께하는 국제 대회. 2026년 세 도시에서 열린다.</p>
    <div class="events-grid">
      <div class="event-card">
        <div class="event-month">May 2026</div>
        <div class="event-emoji">🗼</div>
        <div class="event-name">Champions Clash</div>
        <div class="event-location">📍 도쿄, 일본</div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-card blue">
        <div class="event-month">Jul–Aug 2026</div>
        <div class="event-emoji">🌙</div>
        <div class="event-name">Midseason Championship</div>
        <div class="event-location">📍 리야드, 사우디아라비아</div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-card green">
        <div class="event-month">Dec 2026</div>
        <div class="event-emoji">🐉</div>
        <div class="event-name">World Finals</div>
        <div class="event-location">📍 중국</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- REGIONS -->
  <section class="section fade-up" id="regions">
    <div class="section-tag">Regions & Teams</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">전 세계<br>참가 팀</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">NA, EMEA, 아시아, 중국 4개 지역의 최강 팀들이 경쟁한다.</p>
    <div class="regions-grid">
      <div class="region-card">
        <div class="region-flag">🇺🇸</div>
        <div class="region-name">North America</div>
        <ul class="region-teams">
          <li>Spacestation Gaming</li>
          <li>Team Liquid</li>
          <li>Dallas Fuel</li>
          <li>Disguised</li>
          <li>Lunex Gaming</li>
          <li>Gorilla's Disciples</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card">
        <div class="region-flag">🌍</div>
        <div class="region-name">EMEA</div>
        <ul class="region-teams">
          <li>Twisted Minds</li>
          <li>Al Qadsiah</li>
          <li>Virtus.pro</li>
          <li>Anyone's Legend</li>
          <li>Geekay Esports</li>
          <li>Team Peps</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card">
        <div class="region-flag">🌏</div>
        <div class="region-name">Asia</div>
        <ul class="region-teams">
          <li>Korea Top 4</li>
          <li>Japan Top 3</li>
          <li>Pacific Top 1</li>
          <li>아시아 토너먼트 진출</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="region-card">
        <div class="region-flag">🇨🇳</div>
        <div class="region-name">China</div>
        <ul class="region-teams">
          <li>파트너 프로그램 합류</li>
          <li>2026 신규 추가</li>
          <li>World Finals 개최</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- SCHEDULE -->
  <section class="section fade-up" id="schedule">
    <div class="section-tag">Schedule</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">2026 시즌<br>주요 일정</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Stage 1부터 World Finals까지, 놓치지 마세요.</p>
    <div class="schedule-list">
      <div class="schedule-item">
        <div class="schedule-date">Feb 8–15, 2026</div>
        <div class="schedule-name">Pre-Season Bootcamp</div>
        <div class="schedule-location">서울, 한국 (T1 HQ)</div>
        <span class="badge">완료</span>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-item">
        <div class="schedule-date">Mar 21 – Apr 12, 2026</div>
        <div class="schedule-name">Stage 1 — NA & EMEA</div>
        <div class="schedule-location">온라인</div>
        <span class="badge">진행 중</span>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-item">
        <div class="schedule-date">May 2026</div>
        <div class="schedule-name">Champions Clash</div>
        <div class="schedule-location">도쿄, 일본</div>
        <span class="badge blue">예정</span>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-item">
        <div class="schedule-date">Jul–Aug 2026</div>
        <div class="schedule-name">Midseason Championship</div>
        <div class="schedule-location">리야드, 사우디아라비아</div>
        <span class="badge blue">예정</span>
      </div>
      <div class="schedule-item">
        <div class="schedule-date">Dec 2026</div>
        <div class="schedule-name">World Finals</div>
        <div class="schedule-location">중국</div>
        <span class="badge blue">예정</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- PRIZE -->
  <section class="section fade-up" id="prize">
    <div class="section-tag">Prize Pool</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">챔피언에겐<br>그에 걸맞은 보상을</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">각 스테이지마다 주어지는 상금. 최고가 되어 가져가라.</p>
    <div class="prize-section">
      <div class="prize-amount">$75,000</div>
      <div class="prize-label">스테이지별 상금 (NA + EMEA 각각)</div>
      <div class="prize-detail">
        <div class="prize-detail-item">
          <div class="prize-detail-num">$150K</div>
          <div class="prize-detail-desc">스테이지 합산 총 상금</div>
        </div>
        <div class="prize-detail-item">
          <div class="prize-detail-num">6팀</div>
          <div class="prize-detail-desc">스테이지당 수혜 팀</div>
        </div>
        <div class="prize-detail-item">
          <div class="prize-detail-num">3회</div>
          <div class="prize-detail-desc">국제 라이브 이벤트</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-logo">OW<span>CS</span></div>
    <div class="footer-text">© 2026 Blizzard Entertainment. Overwatch Champions Series.</div>
    <div class="footer-text">비공식 팬 페이지 · 정보 출처: Blizzard, Liquipedia</div>
  </footer>

  <script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
